name: SetUtils_unmodifiableSetTest
description: Unit tests for the unmodifiableSet method in SetUtils.

test_cases.name: testUnmodifiableSetWithNull
test_cases.description: Tests the unmodifiableSet method with a null array, expecting a null result.

test_cases.name: testUnmodifiableSetWithEmptyArray
test_cases.description: Tests the unmodifiableSet method with an empty array, expecting an empty set.

test_cases.name: testUnmodifiableSetWithNonEmptyArray
test_cases.description: Tests the unmodifiableSet method with a non-empty array, expecting a set with the correct elements.

test_cases.name: testUnmodifiableSetWithDuplicates
test_cases.description: Tests the unmodifiableSet method with an array containing duplicates, expecting a set with unique elements.

test_cases.name: testUnmodifiableSetWithMixedTypes
test_cases.description: Tests the unmodifiableSet method with an array containing mixed types, expecting a set with the correct elements.
